MELUN VILLAROCHE,LFPM,FR,4836.272N,00240.528E,84.0m,5,283,1972.0m,45.0m,121.100,"AD prohibited for gliders and aerostats.\nAD reserved for radio-equipped ACFT.\nAD prohibited for class 1,2 and 5 ULM and any ULM not equipped with radio and transponder.\nAD use between 2200-0600 local time subject to authorization from the AD operator, PN 48HR.\n\nTraining patterns reserved for home-based ACFT, prohibited on weekends and public HOL.\nMandatory flight intentions before taxiing, on FREQ TWR.\nTransit overhead AD: minimum recommended transit altitude in the presence of traffic in the RWY circuit: 1800ft AMSL.\nHandling mandatory for non based ACFT whose MTOW is greater than 3 t."
