SOLLIERES SARDIERES,LFKD,FR,4515.233N,00648.067E,1297.0m,2,193,705.0m,60.0m,123.500,"AD reserved for pilots complying with one of the following conditions :\n- based or based on neighbouring AD (see 1) and authorized by an instructor (or holding an instructor’s licence),\n- holding a licence for mountain flights.\nAD available for HEL and ULM.\nFor ULM pilots, it is advised to have followed the mountain course organized by the FFPLUM.\n\n(1)  Neighbouring AD :\nALBERTVILLE, ANNECY, ANNEMASSE, BARCELONNETTE, CHAMBERY AIX LES BAINS, CHAMBERY CHALLES LES EAUX, CHATEAU ARNOUX, COURCHEVEL, GAP, GRENOBLE LE VERSOUD, L’ALPE D’HUEZ, MEGEVE, MERIBEL, MONTDAUPHIN, SAINT JEAN EN ROYANS, SAINT REMY, SALLANCHES, SISTERON."
